    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Locked inside a computer called Proxyma, you must finish its 13-levels game to be completely free. Proxyma is a retro-style 2D platformer with increasingly hard levels where you have to run, jump on various platforms and drop bricks to destroy enemies, open gates and reach for the end. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 13 levels with increasing difficulty; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Three lives per run;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two modes: easy and hard (no continues);</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Run, jump and brick-drop;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Trampolines;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Various platform types (moving, falling etc.);</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Retro-style graphics.</p></li></ul>",
